f4 Rxa8 (13... Nb4 {doesn't change the outcome of the game} 14. fxe5 Nxc2+ 15.
Kf2 Rxa8 16. Bc4+ Ke8 17. exf6 Nxe3 18. Kxe3 (18. fxg7 $143 Nxd1+ 19. Kg3 Kd7
