{[%mdl 8192] C41: Philidor Defence} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 Bg4 4. Be2 $146 (
4. dxe5 Qe7 (4... Bxf3 5. Qxf3 dxe5 6. Qb3 b6 7. Bc4 Qf6 8. Nc3 Bc5 9. O-O Ne7
10. Nb5 Bd6 11. Bd5 Nxd5 12. Qxd5 c6 13. Nxd6+ Kd7 14. Qxf7+ {1-0 (14)
Lajthajm,B (2511)-Colovic,D (2356) Senta 2007}) (4... Nc6 5. exd6 Bxd6 6. Bb5 (
6. h3 Bh5 7. Bb5 Qe7 8. Qe2 Nf6 9. g4 Nxg4 10. hxg4 Bxg4 11. Be3 O-O 12. Bxc6
bxc6 13. Nbd2 Rab8 14. Bd4 Bf4 15. O-O-O Rfd8 16. Rhg1 Rxd4 17. Rxg4 Rxe4 18.
Rdg1 Rxe2 19. Rxg7+ Kh8 {0-1 (19) Cooper,J (2345)-Hodgson,J (2285) Chester 1979
}) (6. Be2 Qe7 7. Nfd2 h5 8. h3 Bxe2 9. Qxe2 Nf6 10. Nc3 O-O-O 11. O-O Nd4 12.
Qd1 Qe5 13. f4 Qc5 14. Kh1 Ng4 15. Nf3 Ne6 16. f5 Bg3 17. Qe2 Nd4 18. Be3 Be5
19. Qe1 b6 20. Bxd4 Bxd4 {Gazik,I (2455)-Horvath,I (2360) Zalaegerszeg 1991 1/
2-1/2}) 6... Qe7 7. Bxc6+ bxc6 8. O-O Rd8 9. Qe2 Nf6 10. Re1 Nd7 11. h3 Bxf3
12. Qxf3 O-O 13. Bf4 Ne5 14. Qg3 Rb8 15. b3 f6 16. Nd2 Rfd8 17. Rad1 Bb4 18.
Rf1 Bxd2 19. Rxd2 {Oliva Castaneda,K (2488)-Guezennec,F (2228) Barcelona 2015
1-0 (47)}) 5. Qd5 c6 6. Qxd6 Qxd6 7. exd6 Bxd6 8. Nbd2 Nd7 9. Nc4 Bc7 10. Ne3
Ngf6 11. Nxg4 Nxg4 12. Bc4 O-O 13. Ng5 Rae8 14. f3 Ngf6 15. O-O h6 16. Nh3 g5
17. Be3 Nxe4 18. fxe4 Rxe4 {Pillsbury,H-Blackburne,J England 1900 1/2-1/2 (67)}
) 4... Nd7 5. h3 Bxf3 {Black forks: g2+e4} 6. Bxf3 Ngf6 7. Be3 Be7 8. c3 O-O 9.
Nd2 a6 10. O-O c6 11. d5 cxd5 12. exd5 Rc8 13. c4 (13. a4 Ne8 $14) 13... h6 {
Prevents intrusion on g5} (13... Ne8 14. Qb3 f5 15. Nb1 $11) 14. b3 (14. Qb1
Re8 $14) 14... Re8 (14... Nh7 15. b4 $11) 15. Re1 Nc5 16. Bxc5 (16. Qc2 $5 $14)
16... Rxc5 $11 {Opposite coloured bishops appeared} 17. b4 {White threatens to
win material: b4xc5} Rc7 18. Qb3 Qd7 19. a4 Rec8 20. a5 {This push gains space}
g6 {Black has a cramped position} 21. Rac1 Kg7 22. Ra1 h5 23. Re3 (23. Rad1 Bf8
$11) 23... Nh7 {White has an active position} 24. Rc3 f5 25. Be2 e4 {Black
gains space} 26. g4 $2 (26. Rd1 $142 $5 $11 {is the best option White has})
26... Bf6 27. gxh5 g5 (27... Qe7 28. Rd1 Bxc3 29. Qxc3+ Kh6 30. Qg3 $17) 28.
Ra3 Bxc3 29. Qxc3+ Nf6 30. Qg3 $2 (30. f3 $142 $5 $15 {is a viable option})
30... Kh6 $17 31. f4 (31. h4 Rg8 32. Kf1 Qe7 $17 (32... Nxh5 $6 33. hxg5+ Rxg5
34. Qh2 $11)) 31... Rg8 $19 32. Kh1 (32. Kf2 $142 Qe7 33. fxg5+ Rxg5 34. Qf4
$19) 32... Nxh5 33. Bxh5 Kxh5 34. Qf2 Qg7 (34... Qd8 $5 {makes it even easier
for Black} 35. Nf1 Rcg7 36. Rg3 $19) 35. Rg3 Qa1+ (35... Qf6 36. Qe2+ g4 37.
Kg1 $19) 36. Kg2 (36. Kh2 Qb2 $19) 36... Rcg7 37. Qe2+ Kh6 38. Kh2 $4 {White
falls apart} (38. Qe3 g4 39. Kf2 $19) 38... gxf4 39. Rxg7 Rxg7 40. Nf1 Qd4 41.
b5 (41. Ng3 {doesn't change anything anymore} fxg3+ 42. Kh1 f4 43. Qf1 f3 44.
Qc1+ Kh5 45. Qg1 g2+ 46. Qxg2 Rxg2 47. c5 Qd1#) 41... Qg1# 0-1

