Bxd5 $4 {makes life more difficult} (31... Qxd5 $142 {nails it down} 32. f3
cxd4 $19) 32. dxc5 $15 Qxc5 {Black has the pair of bishops. .} 33. Qc1 Qe7 34.
Bxg7 Kxg7 35. Ng2 (35. Qd1 Qe4 36. f3 Qe3+ 37. Kg2 Be6 38. Qa1+ Kg8 $17) 35...
