23. Bb2 $4 {ruins a clearly superior position} (23. Rxd5 $142 f5 24. Rxd8 Rxd8
25. Qe2 $16) 23... Nxb2 (23... f5 {seems even better} 24. Qe1 Bb4 25. Qe2 $19)
